   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Khai Vy Project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Khai Vy Corporation (Khai Vy) and Duyen Hai Corporation (Duyen Hai)  known collectively as KVC or the group  together produce and export outdoor and indoor furniture to the Asian, European and North American markets and employ 6,200 workers in four operating sites across Vietnam.  Total export market for the group is split 70% to European market, 25% to U.S. market and 5% to Asia.  The group has its main factory in Ho Chi Minh City and three others are located in Binh Dinh Province.  

By investing in this project, IFC will be providing longer-term financing to help a low cost Vietnamese company maintain its competitive edge while upgrading its operations, and improving environmental, social and corporate governance practices.</narrative>
  </description>
